      <title>印度在马尔代夫附近开设新海军基地，因关系紧张并关注北京</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-opens-new-naval-base-near-maldives-amid-tense-ties-with-eye-beijing-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度周三在靠近马尔代夫的印度洋岛屿上开设了一个新的海军基地，印度与马累的关系仍然紧张，新德里再次与中国争夺在该地区的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-opens-new-naval-base-near-maldives-amid-tense-ties-with-eye-beijing-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:23:39 GMT</pubDate>
